name: Sierra
description:
In Celebration of OBJKT4OBJKT 3rd edition event. 

Sierra has traveled the Universe but cannot escape the things she knows and the experiences she has endured. 

This is an AI GAN portrait developed using dozens of traits, each adjusted by me, and then post-processed and digitally painted.
